{"tid":2378574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得陳錦鴻值得囉視帝？","createTime":"2021-01-24T15:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T15:02:28.000Z","uid":121087,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87ee54e368b9f85851fcbd5262c2462c3b127f6b","tid":2378574,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"無論係老實人 奸角 <br />\n<br />\n陳錦鴻都可以完美演繹<br />\n<br />\n老實人例子有巴不得爸爸 團圓<br />\n<br />\n入面果種戇直只有佢先演得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n創世紀就係佢封神之作<br />\n<br />\n許文彪由遵守規則 好人 慢慢受世界現實摧毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 漸變成不摘手段 乜都做得出既奸角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果種微妙既轉變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真 成個 tvb 根本就無人 carry 到<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76b814bc0052223f2271641224bf0cf4f7e54b7","tid":2378574,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"大冬瓜"},{"pid":"73edb2b66fc961bef85c3681914dee79564e089b","tid":2378574,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"硬起"},{"pid":"87cffadeeb27d0e0907a59c686191944a19b7c39","tid":2378574,"uid":193476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"視帝同演技有咩關係？"},{"pid":"d63201aff86421691469e6b8ea6687b36d85b77f","tid":2378574,"uid":121087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87cffadeeb27d0e0907a59c686191944a19b7c39","tid":2378574,"uid":193476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"視帝同演技有咩關係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"做得帝 姐係萬中無一 <br />\n<br />\n有邊個可以做到佢咁既水平"},{"pid":"4fb8752cc6